FBIS3-25545 "drafr036_a_94015" FBIS-AFR-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 February 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Curfew Announced in Dead Minister's Home Region EA2202205594 Kigali Radiodiffusion Nationale de la Republique Rwandaise in French 1800 GMT 22 Feb 94 EA2202205594 Kigali Radiodiffusion Nationale de la Republique Rwandaise Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] Following the climate of insecurity that prevails in Butare, the prefecture security council has decided on a temporary curfew from 2000 to 0500 throughout the prefecture.
